Package: MBBEFDLite
Type: Package
Title: Statistical Functions for the Maxwell-Boltzmann-Bose-Einstein-Fermi-Dirac
    (MBBEFD) Distribution as Used in Insurance Modeling
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person(given="Avraham", family="Adler",role=c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    email="Avraham.Adler@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3039-0703"))
Description: This package provides probability mass, distribution, quantile, and
    random variate generation for the MBBEFD distribution used in insurance
    modelingas described in Bernegger (1997) <doi:10.2143/AST.27.1.563208>
    without any dependencies.
License: MPL-2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
Suggests: tinytest, covr
ByteCompile: yes
NeedsCompilation: yes
UseLTO: yes
